(go to preferences in hotkeys, changable)




h: subtitle delay
g: subtitle early
v: subtitle track switch , off

e: next frame(frame by frame)


w: full screen window ##
f: switch full screen
o: original size or fit to screen

t: show time

[ : speed slow
] : speed fast
= : speed 1.0x


a: aspect ratio
c: crop

j: audio delay -
k: audio delay +
b: audio track switch

m: mute / unmute

space : pause / unpause
n: next
p: previous
s: stop
l: loop all/one/off

----
S : screenshot



shift + left/right : very short
alt + left/right : short

ctrl + left : medium
alt + ctrl + left : long

up / down : volume
